# Example recommendation result

For visitor `V1`, the prototype recommends:

```text
POI: P4 — Greek Coin Collection
Destination: R4 — Coins and Trade Gallery
Reason: related to inferred archaeology/ceramics/ancient interests.
Shortest path: C1 → R2 → R4
Crowd-aware path: C1 → R2 → C2 → R4
Explanation: the direct gallery passage is shorter but crowded; the recommended crowd-aware route avoids part of the congestion.
```

This demonstrates the first objective of the tool: joint POI and path recommendation from the G-SITM graph.
